    "description": "<strong>It's time for a pawsome beach adventure!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321740/extras/b1599aff6973124d5edfa5964d459662.poster.avif?t=1680540105\" width=600 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321740/extras/b1599aff6973124d5edfa5964d459662.webm?t=1680540105\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321740/extras/b1599aff6973124d5edfa5964d459662.mp4?t=1680540105\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You play as Hank, a drooling stray cat, who loves the beach. And cheeseburgers (or any other food really). Life would be perfect if he finally found his one true love. After setting paw on Stabby Island to go on an eating frenzy, our little chonky boy disrupts the established order of the beach. Can he stuff his belly without consequences? Will he be alone forever?<br><br><strong>Features</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 2D side-scrolling adventure with a wholesome, but kinda dumb story.<br></li><li> 18 accessible levels full with platforming puzzles.<br></li><li> Over 1000 food items to inhale. Some are well hidden!<br></li><li> Shoot garbage at seagulls, crabs and other enemies.<br></li><li> Six mean bosses who are waiting for you to miss that jump.<br></li><li> Full controller support.<br></li><li> Cats!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321740/extras/c1e31105cd3405d1f0857cdc0e078de1.avif?t=1680540105\" width=600 height=120 /></span>",
